text: Gábor Kecskeméti (30 January 1912 - 23 September 1981) was a Hungarian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1912 births Category:1981 deaths Category:Hungarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:People from Békés
